{"tid":581364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又出事！膠袋纏電網 往武漢高鐵杭州冇電死火","createTime":"2018-03-05T09:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T03:26:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fce042c67ba7da47c79b2a456c0dc896d2424272","tid":581364,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520238500_ba90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520238500_ba90.jpg&h=667dfab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520238501_4c86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520238501_4c86.jpg&h=fe01f9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣深高鐵今早發生大範圍停駛，在浙江杭州亦有一列高鐵因為電力線路故障，被迫停在車站。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的是從溫州南站開往武漢的G590次高鐵，今早9時許列車駛至杭州東站時突然死火，車上的燈光全部關閉，乘客滯留在車上。<br />\n<br />\n車上乘客稱，列車上的廣播稱，因為有一個膠袋纏住電網，令到線路出現問題，令列車駛，當局目前已派人前往搶修。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180305/57907362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907362&d=mR%2Fc%2Bzps6cEDNrZ8EtMDxTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e898a1af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907362&h=7e811b1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180305/57907362</a>"},{"pid":"805f9a8a39e5ab05c963a7291921b13f3108fea1","tid":581364,"uid":132557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"膠袋&gt;&gt;&gt;大殺傷力武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa